THIRD-PARTY COMPONENTS
----------------------
UnitAutogen is designed to operate together with the open-source tSQLt
framework.  tSQLt is the work of its own authors, is licensed separately
under its own terms, and is NOT included in or distributed with this
repository.

UnitAutogen v0.13 bundles and redistributes Microsoft's
Microsoft.SqlServer.TransactSql.ScriptDom assembly (the NuGet package
"Microsoft.SqlServer.TransactSql.ScriptDom") in clr/lib/ so the SQLCLR
predicate parser installs without an external download.  That assembly is
the work of Microsoft Corporation and is licensed by Microsoft under the
MIT License, which permits redistribution; it is NOT covered by this
project's AGPL licence.  Its licence and provenance are recorded in
clr/THIRD-PARTY-NOTICES.txt.  UnitAutogen does not modify the assembly.

UnitAutogen is developed and tested against the Microsoft AdventureWorks,
Northwind, and WideWorldImporters sample databases.  These sample
databases are likewise NOT included in or redistributed with this
repository.  They are referenced only as test fixtures during
development; users of UnitAutogen supply their own databases when
running the framework against real production code.


